OL,4,G2100FThe Miracle Club
OL,5,     G1967. Three Dublin wives and a
OL,6,     Gprodigal daughter hope to heal
OL,7,     Gtheir lives in Lourdes.
OL,8,G2225FPersonal Cinema: Maggie Smith
OL,9,     GIn a programme first broadcast in
OL,10,     G1970, Maggie Smith talks to
OL,11,     GMichael Aspel about her career
OL,12,     Gand chooses scenes from some of
OL,13,     Gher favourite films.
OL,14,G2255FTea with Mussolini
OL,15,     GItalian lad Luca, part-raised by
OL,16,     GEnglish ladies living in Florence
OL,17,     Gin 1935, re-enters their lives
OL,18,     Gjust as the encroaching war sees
OL,19,     Gthem forcibly relocated.
